Package org.forgerock.openam.entitlement.rest

Class SubjectTypesResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.entitlement.rest.SubjectTypesResource
  • public class SubjectTypesResource
extends Object
    Allows for CREST-handling of stored EntitlementSubjects. These are unmodfiable - even by an administrator. As such this endpoint only supports the READ and QUERY operations.
    See Also:
    ConditionTypesResource
